pageContext.claim: “Robert Mueller and Leakin’ Lyin’ James Comey are Best Friends, just one of many Mueller Conflicts of Interest. And bye the way, wasn't the woman in charge of prosecuting Jerome Corsi (who I do not know) in charge of ‘legal’ at the corrupt Clinton Foundation? A total Witch Hunt...”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence former FBI director James Comey leaked classified information. Comey has also denied being friends with Mueller, although they worked together when Mueller was FBI director and Comey was deputy attorney general under President George W. Bush. "I don't know his phone number, I've never been to his house, I don't know his children's names. I think I had a meal once alone with him," Comey testified to a House committee. "We're not friends in any social sense.” Also, Trump claims not to know birther conspiracy theorist Jerome Corsi, but Corsi told NBC he has spoken to Trump by phone on several occasions. (We express no view on who is more believable out of Corsi and Trump.)
